snippet.title: Johnny Depp and Amber Heard officially divorced! It's OVER!
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp and Amber Heard's marriage is officially ended. Spouses entered into an arrangement under which the actress will get about 10 millions dollars. Couple endured together less than 15 months as a marriage. Here are the scenes of their tumultuous relationship.

Watch more at: http://amberheardfansite.blogspot.com/

_____________________________________________________________

Music:

Kai Engel - When the lights came on
Podington Bear - Afterglow
